lastCommitMessage: feat: integrate global error handling for SDK and enhance checkout page
- Updated the agora_market_dart_sdk reference to the latest commit for improved functionality.
- Implemented a global error handler for SDK to manage authorization errors, including a mechanism to clear tokens and redirect users to the login page.
- Added a missing required parameter for shipping company in the checkout page.
These changes enhance error management and improve the user experience during the checkout process.
